com.veepoo.protocol

类 VPOperateManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.veepoo.protocol.VPOperateManager

  • public final class VPOperateManager
extends java.lang.Object
    • 【Focus】

      The main class that needs to be operated

      The device does not support asynchronous operations. When multiple time-consuming operations are performed simultaneously, data may be confusing.

      Therefore, had better not do multiple operations at the same time

      SDK Version:2.1.22.15

    • 【重点关注】

      主要操作类,也是唯一需要操作的类

      设备不支持异步操作,当多个耗时操作同时进行时,可能会导致数据紊乱;

      因此在与设备进行交互时,尽可能避免多个操作同时进行

      SDK Version:2.1.24.15

      • Created by timaimee on 2019/07/08.
